text: Mariusz Dąbrowski (born 18 November 1976) is a Polish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 69 kg at the 2000 Summer Olympics.Mariusz Dąbrowski He was born in Koszalin, Poland. == References == Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Polish wrestlers Category:Olympians for Poland
